{
  "title": "Cheesy Mexican Cheese Stir-fry",
  "description": "A buttery, dense Venezuelan dish with a midnight-craving twist featuring buttermilk and bhuna spices, nut-free-friendly.",
  "cuisine": "Venezuelan",
  "diet": [
